# Laravel Horizon

## When to use

- Installing and configuring Laravel Horizon for Redis queue management
- Setting up supervisors, balancing strategies (auto, simple, false), scaling
- Configuring dashboard authorization, notifications (Slack, email, SMS)
- Tags, silenced jobs, metrics, wait time thresholds
- Production deployment with Supervisor process monitor
- Queue priority with multiple supervisors

## Keywords

`horizon redis queue supervisor balancing auto scaling workers processes metrics dashboard notifications tags deploy`
